or bought stocks,

226
00:19:41,702 --> 00:19:43,745
invested in cicada larva mucin,
snail extract…

227
00:19:43,829 --> 00:19:47,165
And Lion's Mane Mushroom granular powder
and germanium bracelets.

228
00:19:47,249 --> 00:19:49,418
