a grand service before the apocalypse.

243
00:20:31,585 --> 00:20:34,129
How romantic.

244
00:20:34,629 --> 00:20:36,548
To perish surrounded by flowers.

245
00:20:36,631 --> 00:20:39,259
No, they're a cult.
We can't get involved. They're harmful.

246
00:20:39,343 --> 00:20:40,177
Dangerous!

247
00:20:41,762 --> 00:20:44,598
The most harmful thing in my life is you.

248
00:20:46,350 --> 00:20:48,393
Aren't you scared of
what might happen to me?

249
00:20:48,477 --> 00:20:49,936
